citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:20pm on 13 May
2021.
The inspector called and left a voicemail for the registrant upon arriving at the premises. The inspector waited 30 minutes
before calling again and leaving a second voicemail. Neither phone call was returned and the inspector left.
End Section
